data.description: Large 3/2 mobile home with 2048 sqf under air on a 1.1 acre lot. Ready for its new owner to add their finishing touches. Only a 35 minute drive to Albuquerque NM. Roof and AC are both original from 2003, no issues but in older condition. Interior is in great condition, just needs minor updating.
